918
01:01:25,331 --> 01:01:27,055
Anaknya.

919
01:02:10,310 --> 01:02:12,410
Tolong Minggirlah.

920
01:02:12,412 --> 01:02:14,945
Apa yang terjadi?

921
01:02:16,649 --> 01:02:18,915
